> **Info:** For item page elevator, set the `$chunk` parameter to the array value you want treat as the current item.
>
> ~~~ .php
> $elevator = new Elevator(['-foo', '-bar', '-baz'], '-bar', 'foo/bar');
> ~~~
>
> Result:
>
> ~~~ .php
> $elevator = [
>     'up' => 'foo/bar/-foo',
>     'hub' => 'foo/bar',
>     'down' => 'foo/bar/-baz'
> ];
> ~~~